7856 Paul Revere Dr, Jacksonville, FL 32208 is a single family home that contains 1,144 sq ft and was built in 1948. It contains 3 bedrooms and 1 bathroom. This home last sold for $110,000 in May 2022. 
 
The Rent Zestimate for this home is $1,328/mo.
